Cook, how do you know one iota of a drop of knowledge about what was going on in the anti-war movement in the USA? You were too busy writing your notes in the jungle, remember? So how do you know there were &quot;communists&quot; in the peace movement in the US?  You don't know a thing about who blew up what building on what campus, but you try now to say you are an expert.<br><br>
For the record, I was on campus in those days, and those who called themselves &quot;communists&quot; or &quot;maoists&quot;, and man, they were quite different, was about one or two per campus, even Berkeley.  The bombings of ROTC offices was the work of wackos, some think even the CIA or the SSS, but who knows. It definately was not the majority of the anti-war protestors.<br><br>
No protestor felt they were prolonging the war, rather just the opposite. We were creating pressure on Nixon to end the war. Jane Fonda went to Hanoi with that intention, to pressure Nixon to end it, not to bomb it. I know it just galls you to have to face reality, but that reality. The American Majority was against, AGAINST the war in VIET NAM almost from the start. The media, with the blessings of LBJ and Nixon, invented the body bag statistics-game just to try and keep the public interested. The fact is that Mom and Pop America could give a rat's rear about the war, unless their son was in it.  <br><br>
The USA/Presidency played off Ho Chi Minh just like they set up Soddam Insane, one day our ally, the next day we are bombing you and you are the boggie man.  Get it straight Cook, either you were taking notes in the jungle, or on 100+ campuses, but you can't be both.  Frankly, your point of view doesn't seem accurate from either end, in my humble opinion,  but then again, I only read posts here, I don't strut around and act like this is my homepage. Man, you write the most long winded and wordy answers I have ever seen.  I will stop now, don't want anyone to think I am you. I know, I know, you will think I am someone else, another paranoid theme to this site I guess.  You and Edwardo. Post my name, just call me &quot;not a chance&quot; cause I don't need the grief I have seen you guys do to others.
